Apartment for sale in the new residential complex "m3 Saburtalo" New district is located in the Central part of Tbilisi, on a plot of land, between Gelovani Avenue and Bakradze street, on the embankment of the Kura river. The apartment is fully renovated, German plumbing, Italian kitchen, dishwasher, washing machine, microwave. In the courtyard of the kindergarten and English school Buckswood School. Delivery of the first stage  the third quarter of 2021.

Prs.comment:
Newly renovated apartment for sale. 1st floor of a 3storey building. Studio + bedroom, separate bathroom. Total area 55 sq.m.
Individual heating, underfloor heating in the bathroom and toilet, hygienic shower, air conditioning in every room, insulated floor (coniferous substrate + ash parquet). The kitchen is fully equipped with appliances, including a dishwasher. The equipment is new, still under warranty. Egger custommade furniture. There is a balcony with a gorgeous view of the entire city.
The apartment is located in the residential complex "Villa Vake Kaklebi" (top of Bagebi). Closed protected area, around a coniferous forest. Playgrounds, large walking area. There is a shop on the territory of the complex. There is a swimming pool and a gym, but they are not operational.
Price: $ 82,500
